videos.headline: San Diego State scores on opening drive with rushing TD
videos.description: Aztecs' RB Rashaad Penny takes the hand-off and runs it in untouched, for a 13-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Aztecs' RB Penny scores 2nd TD of the game with long run
videos.description: Rashaad Penny takes the pitch, cuts back to the inside, and he turns on the jets for an 82-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Aztecs swap RBs, no problem on 3rd rushing TD
videos.description: Juwan Washington comes in for the second drive and he is able to carry the ball in for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: San Diego St. safety makes incredible int
videos.description: San Jose State QB Montel Aaron throws an interception to Parker Baldwin, who makes a crazy catch. Aztecs get the ball back.

videos.headline: Aztecs' FB Bawden leaps over defender for TD
videos.description: Christian Chapman throws a short pass off the play fake to Nick Bawden and he goes airborne to score the 8-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: San Diego St. scores 4th TD in early rout
videos.description: Aztecs' RB Juwan Washington dives over the top for 1-yard rushing touchdown.

videos.headline: San Jose State gets first TD off trick play
videos.description: The Spartans run a gadget play. WR Tre Walker takes the short pass from Montel Aaron and he throws it to a wide open Justin Holmes who scores the 54-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Aztecs running game can't be stopped on 5th TD
videos.description: Rashaad Penny takes the hand-off and he speeds up field for a 64-yard touchdown. He has three rushing touchdowns in this game.

videos.headline: San Diego States' RB Penny talks about his big game
videos.description: Rashaad Penny dedicated his big night to preparation and his offensive line for the dominant run performance.
